Help Files and Documentation:

Most of the information here is also available on-line 
for a running Web Archiver.


  File                 Contents 
  ---------            --------
  README               This file, overall documentation
  Overview.txt         general description of processes
  Setup.txt            runnig the pvarch command to control and manage
                       the data archiving, layout of databases.
  ApacheConfig.txt     some details of Apache / mod_python configuration
  Plotting.txt         brief description of plotting archived data
  Templates.txt        how to setup "status web pages" with templates
  Alerts.txt           all about email alerts for PVs
  Instruments.txt      all about defining and using Instruments.


 